Only one remote agent can be installed as a service with {{installntservice}} command.

A second remote agent cannot be installed as a service : {code}ERROR  | wrapper  | 2009/09/30 11:21:14 | CreateService failed - The specified s
ervice already exists. (0x431){code}

The Clover AntCommandDecorator incorrectly guesses the position of where the targets start, and the command stops.

When run on windows, the following error occurs:

{code}
Starting to build 'Clover Test - Default'
 ... running command line: cmd.exe clover.fullclean /c call c:\apache-ant-1.7.1\bin\ant.bat -f build.xml clean test -Dclover.skip.current=true -Dclover.optimization.enabled=false -lib 
{code}
